                  To run this package follow required dependenancy 
1.Ubuntu Server 24.04 
2.DeckLink Mini Recorder HD ( Video Card)
3.Decklink Driver version "Blackmagic_Desktop_Video_Linux_14.2"
4.Decklink SDK version "Blackmagic DeckLink SDK 14.2"
5.ffmpeg version 7.0.1
6.Nodejs Version  "v22.18.0"
7.Npm version "10.9.3"


                  Installation Guide
1. Install decklink videocard and driver 
2. Compile ffmpeg with Decklink SDK      ( while compiling make sure that openssl enabled for rtmps communication )
3. install Nodejs with version "v22.18.0"
4. then install npm version with "10.9.3" 
5. download my decklink-rtmp-encoder package put it on /opt directory
6. install required npm packages ( follow server.js file)
